question:
What will be the output when the button is clicked?

Frame f = new Frame();
Button b = new Button("Click");

b.addActionListener(new ActionListener() {
    public void actionPerformed(ActionEvent e) {
        System.out.println("A");
    }
});

b.addActionListener(new ActionListener() {
    public void actionPerformed(ActionEvent e) {
        System.out.println("B");
    }
});

f.add(b);
f.setSize(200,200);
f.setVisible(true);
